item.title: Changelog
item.description: Changelog # All notable changes to this project are documented in this page. The format is based on Keep a Changelog. 1.6.6 - 2024-01-31 # Fixed # Some features are not working well if Trace and Optimize is not attached #876 1.6.5 - 2024-01-29 # Changed # use stable version of NDMF 1.3.0 or later #821 1.6.5-rc.3 - 2024-01-27 # Changed # Reverted NDMF to 1.3.0-rc.3 #858 NDMF 1.3.0-rc.4 or later does not execute Optimizing phase on entering play mode.
